1
00:00:14,633 --> 00:00:20,071
<i>Connecting old words</i>
<i>that have been used up</i>

2
00:00:20,906 --> 00:00:28,813
<i>I just want to convey</i>
<i>my simple thoughts</i>

3
00:00:28,881 --> 00:00:34,251
<i>That day's faint wind blows away</i>

4
00:00:34,320 --> 00:00:38,381
<i>at the castle ruins of yesterday</i>

5
00:00:39,625 --> 00:00:44,528
<i>I'll laugh with you</i>
<i>and live for the moment</i>

6
00:00:45,264 --> 00:00:52,170
<i>Still that incident</i>
<i>will continue to trouble you, right?</i>

7
00:00:53,572 --> 00:00:57,064
<i>That's why it must be good bye</i>

8
00:00:57,143 --> 00:01:04,106
<i>Leaving nothing behind,</i>
<i>let us share what is left</i>

9
00:01:04,183 --> 00:01:11,248
<i>In time, we'll realize</i>
<i>that it was everything</i>

10
00:01:11,323 --> 00:01:17,990
<i>And sadness will touch our cheeks,</i>
<i>creating a river of tears</i>

11
00:01:18,464 --> 00:01:27,964
<i>Trembling thoughts swept into a vortex</i>
<i>and melting away</i>

12
00:01:31,655 --> 00:01:32,349
Byakugan!

13
00:01:41,732 --> 00:01:42,596
Caught'em!

14
00:01:43,200 --> 00:01:46,397
All right! All right!
I'll drag Sasuke back without fail!

15
00:01:46,870 --> 00:01:48,770
Naruto! Hate to tell you this,

16
00:01:48,839 --> 00:01:52,002
but I'm gonna demonstrate
my new Jutsu right here!

17
00:01:53,110 --> 00:01:54,099
Me, too!

18
00:01:55,212 --> 00:01:56,440
Don't be so hasty.

19
00:01:56,980 --> 00:01:59,881
As soon as preparations have been made
to implement my strategy...

20
00:01:59,950 --> 00:02:02,111
we'll make direct contact
with the target!

21
00:02:05,789 --> 00:02:08,349
It looks like they haven't
noticed us yet.

22
00:02:10,560 --> 00:02:12,790
Huh? Sasuke isn't there.

23
00:02:15,699 --> 00:02:17,257
It appears that...

24
00:02:17,334 --> 00:02:18,961
he's inside that "coffin."

25
00:02:45,462 --> 00:02:46,793
What's this?

26
00:02:46,863 --> 00:02:48,558
I poked the bush for kicks

27
00:02:48,632 --> 00:02:51,157
and out comes not even a snake,
but just two bugs.

28
00:02:54,004 --> 00:02:56,097
Hey, wait a minute! Wait!

29
00:02:56,440 --> 00:02:58,408
We didn't come here to fight.

30
00:02:59,142 --> 00:03:01,474
We just came here to negotiate!

31
00:03:02,045 --> 00:03:03,273
Huh, then...

32
00:03:03,347 --> 00:03:05,042
What are they?!

33
00:03:20,964 --> 00:03:23,694
There's no point
to that Smoke Bomb.

34
00:03:23,767 --> 00:03:26,201
You can't run away from me.

35
00:03:26,770 --> 00:03:31,002
It's string that's thinner and stronger
than wire that you can hardly see.

36
00:03:31,341 --> 00:03:33,969
My string is placed all over this place.

37
00:03:35,746 --> 00:03:36,644
Darn.

38
00:03:38,281 --> 00:03:42,149
Those two types of wires
on the trap were on purpose...

39
00:03:43,320 --> 00:03:44,912
It was actually a triple trap.

40
00:03:47,324 --> 00:03:48,484
Darn.

41
00:03:50,727 --> 00:03:53,355
Didn't think they had one
with such ability in the group...

42
00:03:56,500 --> 00:03:58,400
You will be...!

43
00:03:59,202 --> 00:04:01,466
What's going on...? My body...

44
00:04:04,975 --> 00:04:07,773
Nice! Kiba, Shikamaru!

45
00:04:09,279 --> 00:04:11,213
Shadow Possession Jutsu succeeded!

46
00:04:13,150 --> 00:04:16,847
But... There is one with
ability like this, too.

47
00:04:17,120 --> 00:04:20,214
Thanks for getting caught so nicely
in my strategy.

48
00:04:20,457 --> 00:04:23,949
Darn... But...

49
00:04:24,361 --> 00:04:27,558
I have this kind of ability, too.

50
00:04:30,100 --> 00:04:30,998
<i>Where did it come from?</i>

51
00:04:32,235 --> 00:04:33,930
Earth Style Barrier!

52
00:04:35,705 --> 00:04:37,434
Earth Dome Prison!

53
00:04:46,650 --> 00:04:52,589
<i>Squad Mutiny. Everything Falls Apart!</i>

54
00:05:10,173 --> 00:05:11,162
Darn!

55
00:05:11,374 --> 00:05:12,204
Where is this?

56
00:05:12,642 --> 00:05:15,475
Inside of that big guy's barrier.

57
00:05:20,917 --> 00:05:21,645
Darn!

58
00:05:29,159 --> 00:05:33,391
These guys are mine.
I want to recover as much as possible.

59
00:05:34,831 --> 00:05:36,890
Once you're done eating,
catch up with us,

60
00:05:36,967 --> 00:05:38,366
we're going ahead.

61
00:05:45,742 --> 00:05:47,209
Come quickly.

62
00:05:48,078 --> 00:05:50,979
Let us out! You!

63
00:05:51,348 --> 00:05:52,940
Be quiet, Naruto!

64
00:05:56,720 --> 00:05:59,052
From the looks of it,
it just looks like a dirt wall...

65
00:06:00,056 --> 00:06:05,460
It's their Jutsu,
there must be some kind of trap.

66
00:06:07,831 --> 00:06:09,492
I don't know what it's made of,

67
00:06:09,566 --> 00:06:11,727
but we're just going to
have to tear this wall down!

68
00:06:12,569 --> 00:06:14,901
Even though
it's dangerous to be careless,

69
00:06:14,971 --> 00:06:18,202
actually it's more dangerous
to remain silent here.

70
00:06:26,316 --> 00:06:27,442
Tunneling Fang!

71
00:06:54,544 --> 00:06:56,739
<i>The wall is restoring itself...</i>

72
00:07:00,650 --> 00:07:01,412
Hey...

73
00:07:01,751 --> 00:07:02,683
I saw that.

74
00:07:03,253 --> 00:07:05,448
Let us out!

75
00:07:10,460 --> 00:07:13,452
It's not just a dirt wall, after all.

76
00:07:43,660 --> 00:07:44,854
Byakugan!

77
00:07:52,569 --> 00:07:53,797
Th-This is...

78
00:07:54,237 --> 00:07:56,364
What is it? What's happening?

79
00:08:15,258 --> 00:08:19,092
This is bad.
Chakra's getting sucked up...

80
00:08:23,266 --> 00:08:29,364
Darn... I didn't expect that
they would just keep us in the barrier,

81
00:08:29,439 --> 00:08:32,636
but I didn't predict that
they would suck our Chakra either.

82
00:08:40,350 --> 00:08:46,118
Man. How dare they!
Let us out of here already!

83
00:09:14,217 --> 00:09:18,517
<i>I've had a good amount of Chakra.</i>
<i>Thank you for the meal.</i>

84
00:09:32,769 --> 00:09:36,535
I feel like my body energy
is being sucked out.

85
00:09:46,649 --> 00:09:49,209
It won't be good if
we stay like this here, Shikamaru.

86
00:09:50,420 --> 00:09:52,547
<i>It was careless to get caught</i>

87
00:09:52,622 --> 00:09:55,591
<i>before we even figured out</i>
<i>our enemy's powers.</i>

88
00:09:56,292 --> 00:09:58,192
<i>On top of all that...inside here.</i>

89
00:10:02,766 --> 00:10:07,999
Darn! I'm going to make an air hole
before all my Chakra is gone!

90
00:10:08,471 --> 00:10:09,301
Akamaru!

91
00:10:11,674 --> 00:10:12,868
The Food Pills!

92
00:10:27,557 --> 00:10:29,787
Akamaru!
Human Mimicry Ninja Art!

93
00:10:31,661 --> 00:10:33,686
<i>And for me,</i>
<i>Beast Mimicry Ninja Art!</i>

94
00:10:47,877 --> 00:10:49,071
Fang Over Fang

95
00:10:56,085 --> 00:10:58,144
All right! Good going, Kiba.

96
00:11:14,304 --> 00:11:15,965
It's useless...

97
00:11:31,654 --> 00:11:35,351
Darn! It starts to restore
the moment it's hit.

98
00:11:37,894 --> 00:11:39,759
Same with the ground.

99
00:12:04,053 --> 00:12:06,578
At this rate, we won't be able to
keep up for another ten minutes.

100
00:12:07,123 --> 00:12:09,489
We'll lose all our Chakra
and be totally annihilated...

101
00:12:28,211 --> 00:12:31,840
<i>I can't use the Rasengan that</i>
<i>requires extremely difficult Chakra control</i>

102
00:12:31,915 --> 00:12:34,645
<i>especially in a place like this</i>
<i>that sucks the Chakra out of us.</i>

103
00:12:37,153 --> 00:12:38,245
Darn!

104
00:13:09,852 --> 00:13:13,948
Hey, I want you to listen to me!
I want to talk to your leader.

105
00:13:14,991 --> 00:13:20,293
We won't go after Sasuke anymore,
so let us out of here!

106
00:13:20,430 --> 00:13:21,362
Hey...

107
00:13:21,664 --> 00:13:24,224
Shikamaru, what are you saying?

108
00:13:26,336 --> 00:13:28,531
Pleading for your life,
how interesting...

109
00:13:29,238 --> 00:13:34,437
But you guys are my prey,
I can't let you out.

110
00:13:35,345 --> 00:13:40,408
Then... just let me out on my own.

111
00:13:46,389 --> 00:13:48,949
This battle...

112
00:13:49,025 --> 00:13:50,720
is such a pain.

113
00:13:51,127 --> 00:13:54,688
You! Do you know
what you're saying?

114
00:13:55,865 --> 00:13:58,766
Shut up, Kiba, be quiet...

115
00:13:59,135 --> 00:14:00,227
What?!

116
00:14:02,638 --> 00:14:03,969
A split in the group, huh?

117
00:14:05,675 --> 00:14:07,734
Seems like you're the leader, but...

118
00:14:07,810 --> 00:14:11,007
I didn't think you would be
the only one begging for your life!

119
00:14:12,148 --> 00:14:16,812
You really see a human's true nature
when one is pushed to the edge of death.

120
00:14:17,420 --> 00:14:19,320
You're such a low life creature,

121
00:14:19,389 --> 00:14:23,792
you're not qualified to be responsible
for the lives of your platoon members.

122
00:14:29,432 --> 00:14:31,957
<i>I've saved the most</i>
<i>important thing for last...</i>

123
00:14:33,603 --> 00:14:36,970
To abandon Sasuke and
to even sell out on your own platoon...

124
00:14:37,040 --> 00:14:39,270
Is that what it means
to be a Chunin of the Leaf?

125
00:14:41,477 --> 00:14:44,378
<i>Sasuke is a Shinobi of</i>
<i>the Village Hidden in the Leaves.</i>

126
00:14:44,447 --> 00:14:45,675
<i>He is a comrade!</i>

127
00:14:46,349 --> 00:14:48,408
<i>Therefore, I will put my life on the line</i>
<i>to help him!</i>

128
00:14:48,651 --> 00:14:50,380
<i>That's the way of the Leaf Village.</i>

129
00:14:51,220 --> 00:14:55,020
Someone like you deserves to die...
I won't let you out.

130
00:14:55,258 --> 00:14:59,354
Shikamaru! I believed in you,
but now I've lost confidence in you!

131
00:14:59,429 --> 00:15:00,623
Let's take this outside!

132
00:15:00,696 --> 00:15:02,425
Hey, we can't get out!
You fool!

133
00:15:02,498 --> 00:15:04,432
That's why we're in this situation!

134
00:15:04,967 --> 00:15:06,127
What do you mean by "fool"?

135
00:15:06,202 --> 00:15:07,362
I'm just speaking the truth, fool!

136
00:15:07,437 --> 00:15:08,927
Oh! You said "fool" again!

137
00:15:09,272 --> 00:15:11,638
Everybody, be quiet for a second!

138
00:15:15,211 --> 00:15:16,075
Choji?

139
00:15:30,526 --> 00:15:34,690
Now he's squatting down.
What is he thinking?

140
00:15:39,035 --> 00:15:42,801
Hey! Why are you eating snacks
all of a sudden?!

141
00:15:43,239 --> 00:15:45,867
Choji binge eats when he gets upset...

142
00:15:45,975 --> 00:15:48,842
Geez, another useless guy.

143
00:15:49,278 --> 00:15:51,712
It can't be helped!
In this case, Shadow Clone...!

144
00:15:51,781 --> 00:15:52,713
Stop it.

145
00:15:53,616 --> 00:15:56,847
The enemy's Chakra is placed
all over that wall.

146
00:15:57,453 --> 00:16:01,412
Even if you are able to scratch it,
the wall will restore itself right away.

147
00:16:02,158 --> 00:16:04,854
In other words, it's useless
unless we can attack it

148
00:16:04,927 --> 00:16:09,091
with a Taijutsu that has enough power
to destroy this wall with one blow.

149
00:16:09,365 --> 00:16:12,766
Somebody that has a Taijutsu
with greater destructive power than mine

150
00:16:12,835 --> 00:16:14,097
would be Choji, but...

151
00:16:16,205 --> 00:16:17,570
At this rate...

152
00:16:25,014 --> 00:16:27,778
Darn, what do we do!

153
00:16:30,520 --> 00:16:34,320
Neji... I'm sorry, but can you use
the rest of the Chakra you have

154
00:16:34,390 --> 00:16:38,724
to observe the wall behind you
and the wall behind Choji?

155
00:16:39,562 --> 00:16:40,324
I got it.

156
00:16:40,696 --> 00:16:42,891
Shikamaru! You be quiet!

157
00:16:42,965 --> 00:16:43,863
Naruto!

158
00:16:43,933 --> 00:16:45,491
You still don't understand?!

159
00:16:45,568 --> 00:16:48,969
Remember what Shikamaru said
when he gathered everyone!

160
00:16:51,340 --> 00:16:56,277
<i>Even I can't just sit back</i>
<i>and be a sluggard.</i>

161
00:16:56,345 --> 00:16:59,143
<i>Because I'm responsible</i>
<i>for your lives.</i>

162
00:17:00,249 --> 00:17:03,582
Choji, don't raise your voice
too much from here.

163
00:17:03,753 --> 00:17:08,452
Kiba, dent that wall
behind Neji and Choji again!

164
00:17:08,891 --> 00:17:10,358
Y-Yeah...

165
00:17:12,395 --> 00:17:14,659
Huh! I don't fully understand
what's going on,

166
00:17:14,730 --> 00:17:16,129
but I'll go wild one more time!

167
00:17:18,434 --> 00:17:19,526
Tunneling Fang!

168
00:17:24,407 --> 00:17:27,604
Huh! No matter how hard you try,
it's useless!

169
00:17:52,468 --> 00:17:53,901
Huh, I see...

170
00:17:54,003 --> 00:17:55,163
It's over there.

171
00:17:58,407 --> 00:17:59,305
Nej

172
00:18:00,076 --> 00:18:02,704
Mark that spot with the Kunai Knife.

173
00:18:03,112 --> 00:18:05,603
Choji, are you ready?!

174
00:18:06,249 --> 00:18:08,240
Okay! Any time!

175
00:18:08,517 --> 00:18:10,678
All right, let's do this.

176
00:18:11,053 --> 00:18:12,987
What's happening?!

177
00:18:13,522 --> 00:18:18,357
Like I said earlier,
the wall's surface is planted with Chakra.

178
00:18:19,328 --> 00:18:25,528
But even this tough wall could have
an area that have a thin layer of Chakra.

179
00:18:25,601 --> 00:18:27,967
That is what Shikamaru speculated.

180
00:18:29,005 --> 00:18:32,441
How... How did you get all of that?

181
00:18:32,908 --> 00:18:35,308
Think about what happened earlier.

182
00:18:36,512 --> 00:18:39,777
Because he noticed that
there were areas that restored quickly

183
00:18:39,849 --> 00:18:42,784
and others that didn't so quickly

184
00:18:42,852 --> 00:18:45,878
when Kiba and Akamaru attacked
the wall surface.

185
00:18:52,295 --> 00:18:55,162
In other words, he guessed that
those areas that didn't restore quickly

186
00:18:55,231 --> 00:18:56,823
probably has a thin layer
of Chakra.

187
00:18:58,701 --> 00:19:02,728
On top of all that,
by cleverly talking to the enemy,

188
00:19:02,805 --> 00:19:06,832
he figured out the position
of the enemy outside of the wall.

189
00:19:08,944 --> 00:19:13,005
He guessed that
the wall furthest from the enemy

190
00:19:13,082 --> 00:19:16,518
probably had the thinnest point
of Chakra,

191
00:19:16,585 --> 00:19:19,053
so that's what he wanted to confirm.

192
00:19:20,723 --> 00:19:22,088
That's what it is, correct?

193
00:19:25,194 --> 00:19:29,756
<i>I see, in order to trick the enemy,</i>
<i>you must trick your friends first.</i>

194
00:19:29,965 --> 00:19:33,833
<i>I didn't see that there was</i>
<i>such a plan behind that conversation.</i>

195
00:19:34,970 --> 00:19:38,133
<i>Then, Choji realized the plan</i>

196
00:19:38,207 --> 00:19:41,438
<i>and the reason why he was eating</i>
<i>was to replenish his Chakra.</i>

197
00:19:43,279 --> 00:19:44,473
<i>These two...</i>

198
00:19:44,547 --> 00:19:48,483
<i>They haven't been working together</i>
<i>as a team all these years for nothing.</i>

199
00:19:49,018 --> 00:19:50,747
I'm depending on you, Choji.

200
00:19:50,920 --> 00:19:51,477
Yeah!

201
00:19:53,889 --> 00:19:55,618
Expansion Jutsu!

202
00:19:56,592 --> 00:19:58,958
All right, let's go!

203
00:20:06,435 --> 00:20:08,460
Human Boulder!

204
00:20:32,161 --> 00:20:32,889
What?!

205
00:20:52,748 --> 00:20:58,846
Choji... You are awesome, after all!

206
00:21:12,802 --> 00:21:19,901
<i>Once in a long while, once in a while</i>

207
00:21:20,076 --> 00:21:25,605
<i>The remnants of a person</i>
<i>broken by dreams</i>

208
00:21:25,781 --> 00:21:30,844
<i>Look like a mountain</i>

209
00:21:34,156 --> 00:21:41,153
<i>Clinging to the Divine,</i>
<i>clinging to Buddha</i>

210
00:21:41,230 --> 00:21:46,759
<i>The remnants of a person crying</i>

211
00:21:47,169 --> 00:21:50,730
<i>Look like a mountain</i>

212
00:21:52,408 --> 00:21:55,468
<i>Rendezvous with a happy dance circle</i>

213
00:21:55,544 --> 00:21:59,344
<i>This is my victory pose, round and around</i>
<i>(round around)</i>

214
00:21:59,682 --> 00:22:02,617
<i>Shake shake shake</i>
<i>Let's look</i>

215
00:22:02,685 --> 00:22:06,815
<i>With a bye bye rhythm that never ends</i>

216
00:22:15,998 --> 00:22:21,095
<i>Look like a mountain</i>

217
00:22:23,039 --> 00:22:26,304
<i>Look like a mountain</i>

218
00:22:26,709 --> 00:22:29,906
<i>Look like a mountain</i>

219
00:22:30,212 --> 00:22:34,148
<i>Look like a mountain</i>

220
00:22:37,953 --> 00:22:40,421
Huh? What are you saying
all of a sudden, Choji!

221
00:22:40,489 --> 00:22:42,286
There's no way that's possible!

222
00:22:42,358 --> 00:22:43,825
But, Choji is right.

223
00:22:44,026 --> 00:22:46,017
If we keep lagging, we won't be able
to catch up with Sasuke.

224
00:22:46,095 --> 00:22:46,993
But still...

225
00:22:47,063 --> 00:22:48,894
Don't worry. I have an idea.

226
00:22:48,964 --> 00:22:50,226
Choji, are you possibly thinking...

227
00:22:50,299 --> 00:22:51,857
Do you have a plan or something?

228
00:22:51,934 --> 00:22:52,366
Yeah.

229
00:22:52,435 --> 00:22:53,231
Hey! Choji!

230
00:22:53,302 --> 00:22:56,499
That's right!
I have that secret weapon of mine!

231
00:22:56,872 --> 00:23:00,069
Next time:
"Full Throttle Power! Choji Ablaze!"

232
00:23:00,209 --> 00:23:01,904
I'm the one who will defeat that guy!
